==English==
===Noun===
'''[[Jesuit|Jesuit’s]] [[bark]]'''

# {{obsolete}} A medicine for the treatment of [[malaria]] prepared from the bark of various [[Cinchona]] trees and shrubs. The main active ingredient was [[quinine]].

